	(text "(2) LSK389B: bin V_GS @5mA to <5mV; Cu thermal clamp over all 4 cans. IF3602 (InterFET direct) drops en 0.6->0.3nV/rtHz if sourced."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 122.936 -45.974 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "17aa97b9-e713-46de-a220-516798cf65ff")
	)
	(text "(4) 10G resistor: PCB guard ring at BIAS_F potential; clean w/ IPA, no flux residue."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 122.936 -37.084 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "3353572e-f6e3-4314-b808-bc59fa0265ed")
	)
	(text "SEC 5  POWER: cap multipliers on both rails. J7 (DIN41612 3x8+8) to isolators/drivers on dig board - now incl ADC SPI. SEC 6 (y300): LTC2500-32 + LTC6655 + LP5907 on-board, VOUT never leaves the PCB."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 104.394 -21.844 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "5f577333-de60-4bf7-836a-b4e323b21416")
	)
	(text "SEC 3  OPA828 integrator + OPA2210A buffer in loop (designed 1-pole loop: fc 200kHz @G21 / 20kHz @G201, zero 480kHz). RN1 = SMNZ 4x1k: 1+2 = G201 top, 3+4 = G21 top. Bottoms: 10x100R par = 10R (G201), 100R (G21)."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 103.378 -28.194 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "841c978d-9ae7-4cda-961c-b68f88e3fef4")
	)
	(text "SEC 4  BIPOLAR bias servo (leakage flows INTO gate node): DAC chA -> U2B x-2 inverter -> 10G sinks 0..-1nA; DAC chB -> 10G sources 0..+500pA. Filters fc=0.16Hz."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 104.394 -25.4 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "857d71ea-1c3c-4f5b-b9ab-e1f2fc6658fb")
	)
	(text "SEC 7  INPUT PROTECTION + FAIL-OPEN MODE (active). \nQ20/Q21 DN2540 depletion pair (norm-ON, ~3R each) in HI leg; Rg holds Vgs=0. \nHI_P clamp Q22/Q23 (2N4117A) to STAR. On |HI_P|>~0.4V window comp U22 sets latch U23 -> Q24(5401)/Q25(1845) level-shift slams GPROT to -12V in <1us => FETs OFF (true disconnect). U21 trip SSR DELETED: PhotoMOS ~ms turn-on was 1000x too slow vs DN2540 Idss surge into pA clamps. \nK5 DELETED: mode via SSR pairs U24/U25 (direct HI_P->CH_A) + U26/U27 (LO_F->STAR); DIRECT_L high = direct mode; bridge U4-U11 (ex BR_HI/LO now HI_P/LO_F) = chop mode; \nBOTH normally-open => input isolated when unpowered. TBD/VERIFY: (a) U22 window thresh R51-54 + LM2903 input-CM must tolerate HI_P to -0.6V and OD level (may need gnd-ref comp or level-shift); \n(b) RESET_N clears trip latch at power-up; (c) DN2540 Idss sets pre-trip surge into Q22/Q23 & bridge - check AQY221N2M pulse rating; (d) noise: Q20/Q21 Ron adds ~0.32nV/rtHz."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 102.87 -11.43 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "b77d71b4-5a78-479b-b5d5-393b5f2a34ae")
	)
	(text "(3) Signal path HI_IN..GATE_A all-Cu, crimped; no Sn joints inside isothermal block. Guard = STAR, single point."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 122.936 -42.164 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "bf3397ed-ca45-48f7-b69f-371012d977c0")
	)
	(text "NOTES: (1) K3/K4 wired per Panasonic ASCTB14E p.12 (VERIFIED): set coil 10(+)/6(-), reset coil 1(+)/5(-); COM 3/8, reset closes 2+9, set closes 4+7. (2b) MEASURE AQY221N2M off-leakage at 10mV, 25-45C, before committing."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 114.046 -51.054 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "caaa6548-e004-4fce-9272-457078be5de0")
	)
	(text "SEC 1  INPUT: isothermal Cu block. Mode via SEC7 SSR pairs (DIRECT_L): direct (high-Z) / SSR bridge (low-Z). SSR chop U4-U11 (2x parallel AQY221N2M per leg) to 100Hz - no contact EMF, no wear. K3=short/blank. K4=100k cal."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 103.886 -54.864 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "cf8a55f3-bb1f-4ca0-b62f-ca074c148a75")
	)
	(text "SEC 2  LSK389B x8 (4 duals): Q1-Q4 gate A, Q5-Q8 gate B. Id=2.5mA each (I_DSS>=6mA margin), tail 20mA. Cascode VB=2.77V -> VDS~1.7V. Loads 750R + 5mA bleed."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 103.886 -31.496 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "fc25969c-b457-4920-856c-2198ea699949")
	)
